            <p>SCP-002 is a Euclid-class object consisting of a large wooden box (1.7 meters in length, 1.1 meters in width, and 1.3 meters in height).</p>
            <p>The inside of the box appears to be a standard living room furnished with leather furniture and a painting on the west wall. However, upon closer inspection, it becomes apparent that the painting is alive and the leather furniture is made
                of human skin.</p>
            <p>SCP-002 has the ability to create and control various entities referred to as SCP-002-1 instances, which are hostile and extremely dangerous.</p>
